i-themes github-dark-high-contrast","auto_excerpt:\n  enable: true\n  length: 100\n","yml",[44,67,68,78,91],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,69,70,74],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,71,73],{"class":72},"sKpQp","auto_excerpt",[47,75,77],{"class":76},"sMAXC",":\n",[47,79,81,84,87],{"class":49,"line":80},2,[47,82,83],{"class":72},"  enable",[47,85,86],{"class":76},": ",[47,88,90],{"class":89},"sCcAr","true\n",[47,92,94,97,99],{"class":49,"line":93},3,[47,95,96],{"class":72},"  length",[47,98,86],{"class":76},[47,100,101],{"class":89},"100\n",[16,103,104,105,112,113],{},"但在這邊如果要使用自動截斷的方式的話，依照 ",[106,107,111],"a",{"href":108,"rel":109},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Fhexo-theme-next\u002Fissues\u002F1245",[110],"nofollow","官方說明"," 是必須額外安裝套件，也就是 ",[106,114,117],{"href":115,"rel":116},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fchekun\u002Fhexo-excerpt",[110],"hexo-excerpt",[16,119,120,121,124],{},"最後一種方式也是我目前使用的方式，使用的方式很簡單，只需要在文章欄位區塊加上 ",[44,122,123],{},"description"," 就可以了",[37,126,128],{"className":39,"code":127,"language":41,"meta":42,"style":42},"---\ntitle: 我的第一篇部落格文章\ndate: 2020-07-18 14:10:24\ntags:\ndescription:\n---\n",[44,129,130,135,146,156,164,171],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,131,132],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,133,134],{"class":76},"---\n",[47,136,137,140,142],{"class":49,"line":80},[47,138,139],{"class":72},"title",[47,141,86],{"class":76},[47,143,145],{"class":144},"sTRMh","我的第一篇部落格文章\n",[47,147,148,151,153],{"class":49,"line":93},[47,149,150],{"class":72},"date",[47,152,86],{"class":76},[47,154,155],{"class":89},"2020-07-18 14:10:24\n",[47,157,159,162],{"class":49,"line":158},4,[47,160,161],{"class":72},"tags",[47,163,77],{"class":76},[47,165,167,169],{"class":49,"line":166},5,[47,168,123],{"class":72},[47,170,77],{"class":76},[47,172,174],{"class":49,"line":173},6,[47,175,134],{"class":76},[16,177,178],{},"這樣在呈現時，就會自動以你提供的 description 來隱藏其餘內容",[16,180,181],{},[29,182],{"alt":123,"src":183},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-12%2014.14.59.png",[12,185,187],{"id":186},"關閉-powered-by-hexo-next","關閉 Powered by Hexo & NexT",[16,189,190,191,194,195,198,199,202],{},"以我自己來講，其實我不太喜歡這個東西，雖然通常我會關閉，你只需要搜尋 ",[44,192,193],{},"Powered by Hexo & NexT"," 將 ",[44,196,197],{},"true"," 改成 ",[44,200,201],{},"false"," 就可以囉。",[16,204,205],{},"但實際上這是尊重原作者，但我自己是不喜歡這個，剛好官方又有提供，所以就...稍微提一下吧。",[12,207,209],{"id":208},"版權宣告-copyright","版權宣告 (copyright)",[16,211,212,213,216],{},"在 「Powered by Hexo & NexT」上方其實有一個版權宣告 ",[44,214,215],{},"copyright"," 的字眼，以我自己來講我會希望想轉載我文章的人可以附上原文連結，那我就會寫",[37,218,220],{"className":63,"code":219,"language":65,"meta":42,"style":42},"# If not defined, `author` from Hexo `_config.yml` will be used.\ncopyright: 若要轉載文章，麻煩請保留原作者名稱與原始連結。\n",[44,221,222,227],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,223,224],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,225,226],{"class":53},"# If not defined, `author` from Hexo `_config.yml` will be used.\n",[47,228,229,231,233],{"class":49,"line":80},[47,230,215],{"class":72},[47,232,86],{"class":76},[47,234,235],{"class":144},"若要轉載文章，麻煩請保留原作者名稱與原始連結。\n",[16,237,238],{},[29,239],{"alt":240,"src":241},"版權宣告","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-12%2014.21.33.png",[16,243,244],{},"(雖然我文章寫得很廢，都是一推筆記，但還是會希望尊重一下原本的作者，我自己在寫筆記時也都會補上我參考哪些文章而寫出來。)",[12,246,248],{"id":247},"footer-圖示替換","footer 圖示替換",[16,250,251,252,255],{},"其實版權宣告的前面也可以修改其他 icon (預設是愛心)，而且你也可以給予動畫效果，在這邊只需要搜尋 ",[44,253,254],{},"Icon between year and copyright info."," 就可以看到相關設置，這邊我舉例改成其他 icon 並且開啟動畫效果",[37,257,259],{"className":63,"code":258,"language":65,"meta":42,"style":42},"icon:\n  # Icon name in Font Awesome. See: https:\u002F\u002Ffontawesome.com\u002Ficons\n  name: fab fa-accessible-icon\n  # If you want to animate the icon, set it to true.\n  animated: true\n  # Change the color of icon, using Hex Code.\n  color: \"#ff0000\"\n",[44,260,261,268,273,283,288,297,302],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,262,263,266],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,264,265],{"class":72},"icon",[47,267,77],{"class":76},[47,269,270],{"class":49,"line":80},[47,271,272],{"class":53},"  # Icon name in Font Awesome. See: https:\u002F\u002Ffontawesome.com\u002Ficons\n",[47,274,275,278,280],{"class":49,"line":93},[47,276,277],{"class":72},"  name",[47,279,86],{"class":76},[47,281,282],{"class":144},"fab fa-accessible-icon\n",[47,284,285],{"class":49,"line":158},[47,286,287],{"class":53},"  # If you want to animate the icon, set it to true.\n",[47,289,290,293,295],{"class":49,"line":166},[47,291,292],{"class":72},"  animated",[47,294,86],{"class":76},[47,296,90],{"class":89},[47,298,299],{"class":49,"line":173},[47,300,301],{"class":53},"  # Change the color of icon, using Hex Code.\n",[47,303,305,308,310],{"class":49,"line":304},7,[47,306,307],{"class":72},"  color",[47,309,86],{"class":76},[47,311,312],{"class":144},"\"#ff0000\"\n",[16,314,315],{},"接下來你應該就可以看到新的 icon 以及跳動的 icon，這邊我就不貼圖示意，讓各位自己去嘗試哩。",[12,317,318],{"id":318},"頭像",[16,320,321,322,325],{},"最後來講頭像的設置，通常頭像預設是關閉的，你只需要搜尋 ",[44,323,324],{},"Sidebar Avatar"," 然後將頭像圖片 url 填入就可以。",[16,327,328,329,332,333,336],{},"而另外兩個選項分別是 ",[44,330,331],{},"rounded"," 與 ",[44,334,335],{},"rotated","，一個是圓形頭像另一個則是旋轉頭像，我個人是覺得圓形比較好看，而旋轉頭像則是在使用者滑入頭像時旋轉一圈而已。",[37,338,340],{"className":63,"code":339,"language":65,"meta":42,"style":42},"# Sidebar Avatar\navatar:\n  # Replace the default image and set the url here.\n  url: \u002Fimages\u002Favatar.gif\n  # If true, the avatar will be dispalyed in circle.\n  rounded: true\n  # If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.\n  rotated: true\n",[44,341,342,347,354,359,369,374,383,388],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,343,344],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,345,346],{"class":53},"# Sidebar Avatar\n",[47,348,349,352],{"class":49,"line":80},[47,350,351],{"class":72},"avatar",[47,353,77],{"class":76},[47,355,356],{"class":49,"line":93},[47,357,358],{"class":53},"  # Replace the default image and set the url here.\n",[47,360,361,364,366],{"class":49,"line":158},[47,362,363],{"class":72},"  url",[47,365,86],{"class":76},[47,367,368],{"class":144},"\u002Fimages\u002Favatar.gif\n",[47,370,371],{"class":49,"line":166},[47,372,373],{"class":53},"  # If true, the avatar will be dispalyed in circle.\n",[47,375,376,379,381],{"class":49,"line":173},[47,377,378],{"class":72},"  rounded",[47,380,86],{"class":76},[47,382,90],{"class":89},[47,384,385],{"class":49,"line":304},[47,386,387],{"class":53},"  # If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.\n",[47,389,391,394,396],{"class":49,"line":390},8,[47,392,393],{"class":72},"  rotated",[47,395,86],{"class":76},[47,397,90],{"class":89},[16,399,400,401],{},"那由於 NexT 可以設置的地方真的非常的多，所以我只介紹我有改過我目前正在使用的設置，那麼今天鐵人賽就先到這邊，我們下一篇見 ",[402,403],"d",{},[405,406,407],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}",{"title":42,"searchDepth":80,"depth":80,"links":409},[410,411,412,413,414,415],{"id":14,"depth":80,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":80,"text":22},{"id":186,"depth":80,"text":187},{"id":208,"depth":80,"text":209},{"id":247,"depth":80,"text":248},{"id":318,"depth":80,"text":318},"Hexo","2020-10-04 00:00:0